						<p><hi rend="bold">Rājarāja I. Year 17: A.D. 992.</hi> </p>						

						<p>In Grantha characters and seems to be related to No. 134 below. Records a gift of land to the temple of Madhūbid (i.e., Vishṇu) in the village of Tēṉūr <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Jananātha-chaturvēdimaṅgalam by Kōdaṇḍa Chōḷa.</p>						

